{"tid":1905843,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"原來雷曼破產後，股市仲有十日逃生門","createTime":"2020-03-01T13:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T08:57:37.000Z","uid":123335,"like":121,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"32af966979c0e42ae5ba2c6b4798a8ae33176751","tid":1905843,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkpShYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkpShYK.jpg&h=4f4ed354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8KShYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8KShYL.jpg&h=d837beb9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS8LCYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS8LCYL.jpg&h=a1ad56df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>同大家一齊回顧下歷史：</ins><br />\n雷曼 08年9月15日破產 <br />\n當日股市跌左<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> -4.42% </span></strong><br />\n但其實都仲未算金融風暴嗰隻崩盤式大跌 <br />\n<br />\n直至08年9月26日，<br />\n其實股市都仲未大跌 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來足足有有十日逃生門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我依家係度諗，<br />\n與其你日日喺度FF 會股災 miss 晒 d 機會<br />\n不如真係等有實體公司破產嗰陣時先沽貨啦<br />\n驚西咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家話岩唔岩聽 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143c394794eb7a606e5538714616072d6a382b4a","tid":1905843,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"bill gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601d947bea8133e244a7ffa7ab8af0bde9f4c1b2","tid":1905843,"uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"143c394794eb7a606e5538714616072d6a382b4a","tid":1905843,"uid":73241,"